All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlienGrubs
    AlienGrubs is an object of food type Alien Grubs which costs 60 dollars and reduces hunger by 45 points.
    CalceraPhos400
    CalceraPhos400 is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 50 dollars and increases health by 50 points
    CoopersPlanet
    One of the planets that selected crew members can travel.
    Crew
    The class dedicated to the Crew of the game.
    CrewMember
    The super class dedicated to the different CrewMember types.
    EdmundsPlanet
    One of the planets that selected crew members can travel.
    FinalScreen
    The screen that appears when the game is finished or won.
    FoodItems
    The super class of all the food types available in the game.
    GameEnvironment
    The game-engine and game logic.
    GuiManager
    The class that manages all the GUI classes.
    Human
    CrewMember of type human with health 100, special power of avoiding the asteroid when piloting the ship.
    IsoscelesTrapezoidTabbedPaneUI
    The class below changes the size of the tabs from rectangle to trapezoid and also lets the user to change the color of the test used within the tabs.
    Items
    The super class to all the food, medicine, money and spaceship parts in the game.
    KalaxianCrystals
    KalaxianCrystals is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 50 dollars and decreases hunger by 40 points
    LumbarPlanet
    One of the planets that selected crew members can travel.
    MainScreen
    The first screen of the game.
    Martian
    CrewMember of type Martian, whose special power is that he eats less food than the other crewmembers.
    Medic
    Crewmember of type medic, whose special power is that her health gets affected the least, out of all the crew members.
    Medicine
    The super class to all the different medicines in the game.
    MillerPlanet
    One of the planets that selected crew members can travel.
    Money
    class dedicated to the money attribute of the crew.
    Nebula
    Crewmember of type Nebula whose special power is that she is immune to Space plague.
    NeutrinoBombs
    NeutrinoBombs is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 100 dollars and decreases hunger by 70 points.
    NewWorld
    The space outpost screen of the game.
    NZT48
    NZT48 is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 75 dollars and increases health by 60 points
    Osiris
    One of the planets that selected crew members can travel.
    Planet
    Planet class that creates a different planet object
    Popplers
    Popplers is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 25 dollars and decreases hunger by 20 points
    R89
    R89 is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 60 dollars and increases health by 70 points
    RandomEvents
    This class implements all the random events specified in the project specification.
    setupscreen
    The screen which enables the player to select the crew members and name the ship.
    ShipStock
    The screen that displays the Food and medicine inventory to the player.
    Solaris
    One of the planets that selected crew members can travel.
    Sound
    This class provides the functionality in window builder to play sounds.
    Spaceettios
    Spaceettios is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 70 dollars and decreases hunger by 50 points.
    SpaceOutpost
    Default quantity of items found using search method in case of a random event occurs.
    SpaceShip
    class dedicated to the Spaceship feature in the game.
    SpaceshipPart
    class dedicated to the number of space ship parts found attribute of the Crew class.
    StarLord
    Crew member if type starlord, whose special power is that he gets tired the least out of all the crew members.
    StrawberrySmiggles
    StrawberrySmiggles is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 30 dollars and decreases hunger by 25 points
    ThirdScreen
    The main screen of the game that contains all the crew member details, ship details and the action buttons.
    Transformer
    Crew member of type transformer whose special power is that he is the best mechanic out of all the crew members.
